      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Pushed a different approach along the lines of https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/24220#issuecomment-1026298608. It does not increase the scope of `cs_main` and maintains the optimization, while avoiding reacquiring the mutex during IBD for the majority of callers that already hold it.\r\n\r\n> This may also have a silent merge conflict with #22053?\r\n\r\nWith the latest push, if `MaybeSendAddr` no longer holds cs_main it should call `IsIBD`, otherwise clang provides a thread safety warning.",
